packNew :: Rectangle -> Maybe String -> IO (Ref Pack)
packNew rectangle l' =
    let (x_pos, y_pos, width, height) = fromRectangle rectangle
    in case l' of
        Nothing -> packNew' x_pos y_pos width height >>=
                             toRef
        Just l -> packNewWithLabel' x_pos y_pos width height l >>=
                             toRef
